# MeshMonitor API smoke tests for this project.
# Update these variables to match your MeshMonitor instance and routing config.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sendPath = /api/v1/messages
@apiToken = replace-with-token
@channel = 0
@toNodeId = ALPHA
@message = MeshSAG HTTP test message

###
# Swagger UI / API docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/docs
Accept: text/html

###
# Channel send using the default MeshSAG field mapping.
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sendPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "text": "{{message}}",
  "channel": {{channel}}
}

###
# Direct message using the default MeshSAG field mapping.
POST {{baseUrl}}{{sendPath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "text": "{{message}}",
  "toNodeId": "{{toNodeId}}"
}

###
# If you changed MeshSAG field names via MM_MESSAGE_FIELD / MM_CHANNEL_FIELD / MM_USER_FIELD,
# adapt the JSON keys in the two POST requests above before using this file.
